- “Stay until the end for a surprise.”
- “You won’t want to miss what’s coming.”

unless the wording naturally fits and is accurate.

HOUSEKEEPING

Include only relevant housekeeping information:

- session duration;
- whether the session is recorded;
- replay information;
- how to submit questions;
- whether chat is monitored;
- accessibility information;
- technical support;
- whether slides or resources will be shared;
- commercial disclosure.

