- Confirm the popup goal.
- Confirm target pages and excluded pages.
- Verify audience eligibility.
- Verify trigger behavior.
- Verify frequency and suppression logic.
- Verify campaign dates and time zone.
- Confirm all offer details and deadlines.
- Test every CTA and destination.
- Verify form submission and CRM integration.
- Test success and error states.
- Confirm consent and privacy language.
- Confirm cookie-consent separation.
- Verify that optional consent is not preselected.
- Test keyboard navigation.
- Test screen-reader naming and announcements.
- Test focus entry, containment, closure, and return.
- Test visible focus indicators.
- Test zoom and text reflow.
- Test reduced-motion behavior.
- Test desktop and mobile layouts.
- Test portrait and landscape mobile views.
- Verify the close control remains visible.
- Test dismissal persistence.
- Test conversion suppression.
- Test logged-in, subscribed, and purchased-user suppression.
- Test all personalization fallbacks.
- Remove sensitive information.
- Verify image rights and alt text.
- Check page speed and layout shift.
- Check interaction with chat widgets, cookie notices, and other overlays.
